welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Forest City, a charming city known for its scenic beauty and friendly locals. Get ready to explore and experience all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando Executive Airport serves as the hub for all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is exclusively for private flights and offers luxurious amenities for passengers.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy free wifi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando Sanford International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal B
terminals.description: Terminal B at Orlando Sanford International Airport is primarily used for domestic flights operated by Allegiant Air.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network by selecting 'SFB Free WiFi' from the list of available networks.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kissimmee Gateway Airport serves both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Kissimmee Gateway Airport is reserved for private and executive flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: Terminal A at Orlando International Airport serves domestic flights for airlines such as American Airlines, Delta, and United.

terminals.name: Terminal B
terminals.description: Terminal B at Orlando International Airport serves domestic flights for airlines such as JetBlue, Southwest, and Spirit.

terminals.name: Terminal C
terminals.description: Terminal C at Orlando International Airport serves international flights for airlines such as Air Canada, British Airways, and Lufthansa.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport, but a free account must be created to access it.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Jet Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is dedicated for private jet arrivals and departures.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
